template:
System: You are a principal business analyst. Analyze these CRM performance statistics:
- Total Visitors: {visitorsCount}
- CRM Leads: {leadsCount}
- Revenue Target: {monthlyRevenue}
- Active Pipeline Status: {activePipeline}

User: Summarize today's business performance and provide a 3-point operational action plan to improve counselor conversions for Company {CompanyName}.

System: You are an automated lead scoring classifier. Analyze this profile:
- Lead Name: {LeadName}
- Source Channel: {sourceChannel}
- Target Interest: {courseName}
- Last Counselor Note: {lastNote}

User: Compute a conversion probability (0-100%) and suggest the next three critical counseling follow-up actions for {CompanyName}.

System: You are an account retention manager. Review customer profile:
- Customer Name: {CustomerName}
- Enrolled Course: {courseName}
- Onboarding Date: {onboardingDate}
- Placement Progress status: {placementStatus}

User: Analyze interaction timeline logs for customer {CustomerName} of Company {CompanyName}. Suggest potential advanced specialization course packages for upselling.

System: You are an expert CRM automation designer. We need to construct a new workflow.
- Event Trigger: {triggerEvent}
- Filter Criteria: {filterCondition}
- Target Actions: {targetActions}

User: Suggest an optimized action timeline sequence and rule syntax structure for event {triggerEvent} in Company {CompanyName}.

System: You are a principal customer support executive. Review support ticket:
- Customer Name: {CustomerName}
- Ticket Subject: {ticketSubject}
- Severity level: {severityLevel}

User: Draft an empathetic customer auto-reply email for Company {CompanyName} incorporating initial troubleshooting steps: {troubleshootingSteps}.
